╠Peter & Muriel Kenny
We wrote your name In the sand, but the waves washed it away
We wrote your name in the sky, but the clouds blew it away
So we wrote your name in our hearts and forever it will stay"¤
╠In Loving Memory
RONALD HALL                                             LOUISA HALL
25/11/1927           TRUE EASTENDERS       21/11/1930
  TO                                                                         TO
15/10/2003                                                       29/12/2007

Back Together Again
Their life together started the day they met by this lake,
So it seems only right to celebrate their lives by
placing this plaque here
DAD & MUM
If tears could build a stairway and memories a lane
I'd walk right up to heaven and bring ya home again
Luv Ya 124"▄
